[7] Samoa: Updated measles in Samoa
Date: Sun 22 Dec 2019
Source: Government of Samoa (Twitter @samoagovt) [edited]
https://twitter.com/samoagovt/status/1208896015555645440


Latest update: 5552 measles cases have been reported since the outbreak with 32 recorded in the last 24 hours. To date [22 Dec 2019], 79 measles-related deaths have been recorded, with no fatalities in the last 24 hours.

Vaccination update: As of 22 Dec [2019], 94% of population have been vaccinated.

Compiled by ProMED-mail Rapporteur Kunihiko Iizuka:
Date: 22 Dec [2019] - 5552 cases, 79 deaths, 32 increase in the last 24 hours
Date: 21 Dec [2019] - 5520 cases, 79 deaths, 26 increase in the last 24 hours
Date: 20 Dec [2019] - 5494 cases, 79 deaths, 31 increase in the last 24 hours, one additional death
Date: 19 Dec [2019] - 5463 cases, 78 deaths, 39 increase in the last 24 hours, one additional death

